  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;The proposed mansard roof extension, by reason of its scale, detailed design and location within a group of properties with an unbroken roofline,&amp;nbsp; would result in an incongruous and overly prominent extension that would disrupt the symmetry of the terrace and would detract from the character of the host building and surrounding area. The proposal, therefore, fails to comply with policy LP1 (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Design Quality and Local Character) of&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;the Hackney Local Plan (LP33) (2020), Policies D3(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-166be07a-7fff-361c-c127-3e0ec43a3f04&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach) and D4 (Delivering Good Design) of the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;London Plan (2021), and the recommendations of the Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Extensions and Alterations 2009.&lt;/span&gt;"
